com.github.wuic.path

Interface Path

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    DirectoryPath, FilePath
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDirectoryPath, FsDirectoryPath, FsFilePath, SimplePath, VirtualDirectoryPath, WebappDirectoryPath, WebappFilePath, ZipDirectoryPath, ZipEntryDirectoryPath, ZipEntryFilePath, ZipEntryPath, ZipFilePath

    public interface Path

    A path is an element which is could be linked to another path as parent to represent a hierarchy.

    Since:
    0.3.4
    Version:
    1.1
    Author:
    Guillaume DROUET
